This paper focuses on natural language understanding and machine comprehension, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed datasets and formal framework for multi-step reasoning also involve machine learning and computational complexity, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), computational complexity (cs.CC), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
